Here's a checklist:

ROS Core running
RPLIDAR node running and publishing data
Robot state publisher running (if applicable)
SLAM node running (if you're using SLAM)
OAK-D Lite camera connected
All necessary ROS topics being published (check with rostopic list)
Your Python script running

MAIN ISTRUCTIONS:
1)- Rodar ROSCORE em uma CMD;
2)- Em outra janela CMD, rodar: rplidar_ros rplidar_a1.launch (alternativamente)-> roslaunch rplidar_ros rplidar_a1.launch
